00:27:23,430 --> 00:27:24,760
(Gotta protect my favorite couple)
Mix up the rest.

837
00:27:24,860 --> 00:27:26,160
(So exciting!)

838
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:28,110
Please keep watching

839
00:27:28,110 --> 00:27:29,230
Live and Love Season 2 on WeTV.

840
00:27:29,230 --> 00:27:31,350
(Don't forget to follow!)
Let's see how things unfold.

841
00:27:32,780 --> 00:27:49,740
("Live and Love" S2 Release Schedule)

842
00:27:49,740 --> 00:27:51,440
(Balance Island Special Event on Fri. 12 PM.)
Attention, islanders!

843
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:54,310
(Love Aeroplane Chess)
Today, we'll play two rounds.

844
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:56,250
I will win.

845
00:27:56,250 --> 00:27:57,360
(Excited)
Six!

846
00:27:57,430 --> 00:27:58,190
(Luck skipped me this time.)

847
00:27:58,320 --> 00:27:59,770
(Failed to take off in the second round)
Almost got a six.

848
00:27:59,770 --> 00:28:00,400
I'm so mad right now.

849
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:02,160
These two are about to throw down.

850
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:02,850
No way.

851
00:28:02,850 --> 00:28:04,010
(Stops)
I didn't throw just now.

852
00:28:04,090 --> 00:28:05,920
What made you cry last time?

853
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:08,490
Name your partner's habit
you can't stand.

854
00:28:08,490 --> 00:28:10,250
Whose relationship on the island
made you jealous?

855
00:28:10,290 --> 00:28:11,530
I actually know quite a bit.

856
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:13,120
And then I just started crying.

857
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,530
I just can't escape your hold.

858
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:15,830
(Really corny)

859
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:17,050
I will win.

860
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,010
That's hilarious.
